Notification\">5</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"navbarIcon\">\n            <Notifications />\n            <span className=\"navbarIconNotification\">4</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n        { user ? <li>Welcome! </li> : <li> <Link to='/login'> Login </Link></li>}\n    { user ? <button onClick={handleLogout}>Log Out</button> : null}\n \n      <img\n        src=\"/assets/profile/mushu.jpg\"\n        alt=\"profile\"\n        className=\"navbarProfilePic\"\n      />\n    </div>\n\n  );\n};\n\nexport default Navbar;\n\n\n","/Users/farhanahossain/Desktop/SEI/projects/Bunnybook/src/components/Post/Post.jsx",[],[],"/Users/farhanahossain/Desktop/SEI/projects/Bunnybook/src/seeds/Seeds.jsx",[],[],"/Users/farhanahossain/Desktop/SEI/projects/Bunnybook/src/components/CloseFriends/CloseFriends.jsx",["113"],[],"import React from 'react'\nimport '../Sidebar/Sidebar.css'\nimport {Users} from '../../seeds/Seeds'\n\n\nconst CloseFriends = ({user}) => {\n  return (\n    <div>\n    <li className=\"sbfriend\">\n        <img className=\"sbfriendpic\" src={user.profilePicture} alt=\"\" />\n        <span className=\"sbfriendname\">{user.username}</span>\n    </li>\n\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default CloseFriends","/Users/farhanahossain/Desktop/SEI/projects/Bunnybook/src/components/OnlineFriends/OnlineFriends.jsx",[],[],{"ruleId":"114","severity":1,"message":"115","line":1,"column":16,"nodeType":"116","messageId":"117","endLine":1,"endColumn":27},{"ruleId":"114","severity":1,"message":"118","line":2,"column":9,"nodeType":"116","messageId":"117","endLine":2,"endColumn":17},{"ruleId":"114","severity":1,"message":"119","line":2,"column":19,"nodeType":"116","messageId":"117","endLine":2,"endColumn":28},{"ruleId":"114","severity":1,"message":"120","line":3,"column":9,"nodeType":"116","messageId":"117","endLine":3,"endColumn":14},"no-unused-vars","'useNavigate' is defined but never used.","Identifier","unusedVar","'useState' is defined but never 